sequenceDiagram
    actor User as User / Host
    participant fe@{ "type": "boundary" } as Frontend
    participant API@{ "type": "control" } as API
    participant svc@{ "type": "control" } as RoomService
    participant cld@{ "type": "boundary" } as Cloudinary
    participant db@{ "type": "database" } as Database
    participant ms@{ "type": "control" } as Meilisearch

    Note over User,ms: Apply-to-Host (USER role) OR Create Room (HOST role)<br/>Both call roomService.handleRoomCreation()

    User->>+fe: Fill room form + select images
    fe->>+API: POST /room/apply  OR  POST /room/create
    API->>API: verifyToken + checkBanned middlewares

    alt Branch — applyToBeHost
        API->>API: Require role === 'USER'
        alt Already HOST/ADMIN
            API-->>fe: 400 "You are already a Host"
            fe-->>User: Show error
        end
    else Branch — createRoom
        API->>API: Require role !== 'USER'
        API->>+db: findFirst(room where hostId=user, status=PENDING)
        db-->>-API: pendingRoom or null
        alt Has pending application
            API-->>fe: 400 "You already have a pending application."
            fe-->>User: Show error
        end
    end

    API->>+svc: handleRoomCreation(userId, body)
    svc->>svc: Validate body (CreateRoomSchema)

    alt Validation failed
        svc-->>API: ValidationError(issues)
        API-->>fe: 400 with field issues
        fe-->>User: Show validation errors
    else Validation passed
        loop For each image (parallel)
            svc->>+cld: upload(base64/url)
            cld-->>-svc: { image_url, public_id }
        end

        svc->>+db: room.create(<br/>...data, hostId, status=PENDING,<br/>images.create=[{imageUrl, publicId}])
        alt DB create failed
            db-->>svc: Error
            svc->>cld: destroy(public_id) for each uploaded image
            svc-->>API: Throw error
            API-->>fe: 500 / propagated error
        else DB create ok
            db-->>-svc: room (with images, host)
            svc->>+ms: upsertRoom(toRoomDoc(room))
            ms-->>-svc: Indexed (status=PENDING)
            svc-->>-API: room
            API-->>-fe: 201 "Application sent" / "Room created — awaits approval"
            fe-->>-User: Show pending state
        end
    end

    Note over User,ms: Room is in PENDING state — not visible to public<br/>until Admin approves (see admin_approve_room_sequence)
